{
  "index_patterns": [
    "jumplists-*"
  ],
  "composed_of": [
    "settings-common",
    "mappings-corecommon",
    "mappings-string",
    "mappings-final"
  ],
  "template": {
    "settings": {
      "index": {
        "mapping": {
          "total_fields": {
            "limit": 2000
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "mappings": {
      "properties": {
        "jumplist": {
          "properties": {
            "variant":          { "type": "keyword" },
            "app_id":           { "type": "keyword" },
            "app_description":  { "type": "keyword", "fields": { "text": { "type": "text" } } },
            "path":             { "type": "keyword", "fields": { "text": { "type": "text" } }, "ignore_above": 8191 },
            "entry_name":       { "type": "keyword" },
            "has_sps":          { "type": "keyword" },
            "pinned":           { "type": "boolean" },
            "interaction_count":{ "type": "integer" },
            "notes":            { "type": "text" },
            "destlist": {
              "properties": {
                "version":           { "type": "keyword" },
                "last_used_entry":   { "type": "keyword" },
                "mru_position":      { "type": "integer" },
                "entry_number":      { "type": "integer" },
                "creation":          { "type": "date" },
                "mtime":             { "type": "date" }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "file": {
          "properties": {
            "tracker": {
              "properties": {
                "file_birth_droid":   { "type": "keyword" },
                "file_droid":         { "type": "keyword" },
                "volume_birth_droid": { "type": "keyword" },
                "volume_droid":       { "type": "keyword" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "_meta": {
    "provider": "SOF-ELK",
    "purpose": "Jump List output parsed by JLECmd (Eric Zimmerman) from KAPE. Covers both .automaticDestinations-ms (Windows-managed per-AppId recent files including DestList MRU + PinStatus + InteractionCount) and .customDestinations-ms (app-managed jump-list categories like Outlook 'Recent', Chrome 'Most visited', Firefox 'Recent Sessions', PuTTY pinned sessions). jumplist.variant = 'automatic' | 'custom'. Insider-threat angles: removable-media references (DriveType + drive-letter heuristics), UNC/network paths, distributed link-tracker cross-machine signals (MachineID != Hostname), pinned items (explicit user intent), and per-app categorization (Office / browser / remote access / collab / file explorer / settings)."
  }
}
